data.title: Happy Birthday Victory Venkatesh
data.meta_description: Telugu cinema news, Movie reviews, OTT News, OTT Release dates, Latest Movie reviews in Telugu, telugu movie reviews, Box office collections
data.text:
December 13th happens to be the birthday of a man who has Victory in his name. Victory Venkatesh turns 53 today. Born in 1960 into the family of movie moghul Dr. D.Ramanaidu, Venkatesh grew up in Chennai and completed his schooling there. He made his movie debut with the film ‘Kaliyuga Pandavulu’ in 1986 and has quickly established himself as one of the top heroes of the Telugu Film Industry.

He has earned a name for himself as a versatile and talented hero. 7 Nandi Awards and 4 Filmfare awards are a testament to his skill as an actor. Some of his most memorable hits include Bobbili Raja, Swarnakamalam, Shatruvu, Coolie No.1, Kshana Kshanam, Chanti, Dharma Chakram, Preminchukundam Raa, Nuvvu Naaku Nacchav etc.

Venkatesh is a family man to the core and his pleasant nature has earned him many friends in the industry. Venkatesh has now kickstarted the trend of multi-starrers in TFI. He also has a couple of interesting projects coming up next year.

123telugu.com wishes Victory Venkatesh a Very Happy Birthday.
